PLEASE ALLOW 48 HOURS FOR A RESPONSE TO YOUR INITIAL INQUIRY.
ANY INQUIRIES MADE FRIDAY AFTER 2PM WILL NOT BE RESPONDED TO UNTIL THE FOLLOWING MONDAY
PRIVATE DINING EVENTS RESERVATION POLICY:
-ALL PRIVATE DINING AND EVENT RESERVATIONS REQUIRE A SIGNED EVENT CONTRACT. RESERVATIONS ARE NOT GUARANTEED UNLESS CONTRACT IS PROMPTLY RETURNED AND CONFIRMED BY OUR EVENT COORDINATOR
-ALL PRIVATE SPACES HAVE A DEPOSIT AND/OR ROOM RENTAL FEE DUE AT TIME OF BOOKING
-ALL PRIVATE SPACES REQUIRE A PRESET MENU FOR THE RESERVATION
-ALL SPACES HAVE A REQUIRED MINIMUM ATTENDANCE AND/OR FOOD & BEVERAGE MINIMUM
-MENU PRICES STARTING AT:
LUNCH      $24
DINNER     $36
BUFFET      $34
HORS D' OEUVRES MENU AVAILABLE

Sunset Room
Fully private. Flat screen TV with video capabilities through Apple TV or an HDMI cable. Room can hold up to 32 people max. Minimum 12 adults
Capacity:
12-32
Lower Bar
Up to 40 people seated or 70 cocktail style. This screened in space (non a/c) sits right on Lake Shipp and has its own bar. All tables are bar height. Minimum 30 adults
Capacity:
30-65
Main Bar
Back section of the main dining room directly adjacent to the main bar.  Holds up to 44 seated/ minimum 32. This space is NOT fully private. Only available on specific days / times with restrictions.
Capacity:
32-44
